long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Quickly bookmarks the current tab's website into one of a chosen set of favorite bookmark folders.

The default keyboard shortcut is Control-Shift-E (or Command-Shift-E on Mac), but it can be overridden in "Keyboard shortcuts" under "Manage extensions".
